rComments: Gilmour always wanted us to reach our goals. She listened to the goals we had for the semester and gave us necessary feedback to get there. If you go see her in her office hours and speak to her regularly with questions and concerns as well as ensure you incorporate her feedback in your next assignment, you'll do well! Reading is heavy though!
Dr. Gilmour may come off intimidating at first but she really just wants to challenge you to think critically. GO TO OFFICE HOURS AND DO THE READINGS!! She is incredibly helpful!
